4 SYNOPSIS:
5 This bill would designate the Board of
6 Commissioners of the Alabama State Bar as an agency of
7 the Judicial Branch of state government.
8
9
10 A BILL
11 TO BE ENTITLED
12 AN ACT
13
14 Relating to the Board of Commissioners of the Alabama
15 State Bar; to designate the board as an agency of the Judicial
16 Branch of state government.
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
18 Section 1. Section 34-3-43.1 is added to the Code of
19 Alabama 1975, to read as follows:
20 §34-3-43.1
21 The Board of Commissioners of the Alabama State Bar is
22 an agency of the Judicial Branch of state government.
23 Section 2. This act shall become effective on October
24 1, 2026.
